<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 01:17:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Linux 开发者开始取消对已有 37 年历史的 Intel 486 CPU 的支持——负责人 Linus Torvalds 表示继续支持的“真正理由为零”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/linux-devs-start-removing-support-for-37-year-old-intel-486-cpu-head-honcho-linus-torvalds-says-zero-real-reason-to-continue-support</link><description>就现代 Linux 而言，也许是时候让已有 37 年历史的 Intel 486 系统退役了，因为操作系统内核开发人员似乎已经开始取消对这款传奇 CPU 的支持。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/linux-devs-start-removing-support-for-37-year-old-intel-486-cpu-head-honcho-linus-torvalds-says-zero-real-reason-to-continue-support.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 01:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/linux-devs-start-removing-support-for-37-year-old-intel-486-cpu-head-honcho-linus-torvalds-says-zero-real-reason-to-continue-support</guid></item><item><title>在我们银河系的郊区发现了数十条隐藏的星流</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/dozens-of-hidden-star-streams-found-in-the-outskirts-of-our-milky-way-galaxy</link><description>研究表明，为了找到它们，陈开发了一种名为 StarStream 的计算机算法，该算法使用基于物理的模型来搜索流，而不是仅仅依靠视觉模式。研究小组随后将该方法应用于盖亚数据，该数据从 2014 年到 2025 年绘制了银河系中数十亿颗恒星的位置和运动图。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dozens-of-hidden-star-streams-found-in-the-outskirts-of-our-milky-way-galaxy.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 01:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/dozens-of-hidden-star-streams-found-in-the-outskirts-of-our-milky-way-galaxy</guid></item><item><title>发作期 MRI 异常和新发癫痫持续状态后无端癫痫发作的风险</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/peri-ictal-mri-abnormalities-and-risk-of-unprovoked-seizures-after-de-novo-status-epilepticus</link><description>刚刚发表：蛋白质 s-棕榈酰化在癌症中的作用：从动态调节到治疗潜力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/peri-ictal-mri-abnormalities-and-risk-of-unprovoked-seizures-after-de-novo-status-epilepticus.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/peri-ictal-mri-abnormalities-and-risk-of-unprovoked-seizures-after-de-novo-status-epilepticus</guid></item><item><title>旨在记住</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/designed-to-remember</link><description>在一个新的&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/designed-to-remember.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/designed-to-remember</guid></item><item><title>刺激迷走神经如何保护大脑免受阿尔茨海默病的侵害</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-stimulating-the-vagus-nerve-could-protect-the-brain-from-alzheimers-disease</link><description>出现 tau 蛋白缠结并不意味着一个人患有阿尔茨海默病——事实上，几乎每个人都会不同程度地发生这种情况。但由于这些变化始于蓝斑，一些大脑研究人员（包括我自己）将这个区域视为&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/how-stimulating-the-vagus-nerve-could-protect-the-brain-from-alzheimers-disease.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/how-stimulating-the-vagus-nerve-could-protect-the-brain-from-alzheimers-disease</guid></item><item><title>世界上最铁杆的 Jak &amp;amp; Daxter 头目已经完成了整个三部曲的本地 PC 移植</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-most-hardcore-jak-daxter-heads-in-the-world-have-finished-their-native-pc-ports-of-the-entire-trilogy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 00:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/the-most-hardcore-jak-daxter-heads-in-the-world-have-finished-their-native-pc-ports-of-the-entire-trilogy</guid></item><item><title>物理学家利用 37 维光脉冲来证明量子悖论</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physicists-use-pulses-of-light-in-37-dimensions-to-prove-quantum-paradox</link><description>物理学家对三上下文 GHZ 悖论建立了 37 维光学测试，强化了量子上下文的证据。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/physicists-use-pulses-of-light-in-37-dimensions-to-prove-quantum-paradox2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 23:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/physicists-use-pulses-of-light-in-37-dimensions-to-prove-quantum-paradox</guid></item><item><title>对 1,700 种语言的研究揭示了令人惊讶的隐藏模式</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-of-1700-languages-reveals-surprising-hidden-patterns</link><description>对 1,700 多种语言的大规模新分析表明，一些长期争论的“通用”语法规则实际上是真实的。通过使用尖端的进化方法，研究人员发现语言往往以可预测的方式而不是随机地进化。关键模式（例如词序和语法结构）不断在全球范围内重新出现。结果表明，共同的人类思维和沟通压力塑造了所有语言的发展方式。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/study-of-1700-languages-reveals-surprising-hidden-patterns2.webp" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 23:32:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/study-of-1700-languages-reveals-surprising-hidden-patterns</guid></item><item><title>长寿并不相同：为什么延长生命的治疗可能是“生物彩票”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/longevity-isnt-equal-why-life-extending-treatments-may-be-a-biological-lottery</link><description>延长寿命只是衰老研究目标的一部分。科学家还希望更多的人能够健康地度过晚年，并减少个体死亡时间的差异。这种理想的结果通常被描述为“使生存曲线平方”，即大多数死亡被推入晚年的狭窄窗口内，而不是分散在许多年中。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/longevity-isnt-equal-why-life-extending-treatments-may-be-a-biological-lottery.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 23:17:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/longevity-isnt-equal-why-life-extending-treatments-may-be-a-biological-lottery</guid></item><item><title>这个新框架可以使机器人网络、自动驾驶汽车更加安全</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/this-new-framework-could-make-networks-of-robots-self-driving-cars-safer</link><description>研究人员揭示了一种定量方法，衡量一个自主代理（例如车辆或机器人）在做出决策时应该信任另一个代理或数据流的程度。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/this-new-framework-could-make-networks-of-robots-self-driving-cars-safer.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 23:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/this-new-framework-could-make-networks-of-robots-self-driving-cars-safer</guid></item></channel></rss>